quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  23,109,"Dájúdájú igun kan wà nínú àwọn ẹrúsìn Mi, tí wọ́n ń sọ pé: “Olúwa wa, a gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo. Nítorí náà, foríjìn wá, kí O sì kẹ́ wa. Ìwọ sì l’óore jùlọ nínú àwọn aláàánú.”1 {1}",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah as-Sọ̄ffāt; 37:125.]
  23,110,"Ṣùgbọ́n ẹ sọ wọ́n di oníyẹ̀yẹ́ tó bẹ́ẹ̀ gẹ́ tí àwọn yẹ̀yẹ́ (yín) fi mu yín gbàgbé ìrántí Mi. Ẹ̀yin sì ń fi wọ́n rẹ́rìn-ín."
  23,111,"Dájúdájú Mo san wọ́n ní ẹ̀san ní òní nítorí sùúrù wọn; dájúdájú àwọn, àwọn ni olùjèrè."
  25,55,"Wọ́n ń jọ́sìn fún lẹ́yìn Allāhu ohun tí kò lè ṣe wọ́n ní àǹfààní, tí kò sì lè kó ìnira bá wọn. Aláìgbàgbọ́ jẹ́ olùrànlọ́wọ́ (fún Èṣù) láti tako Olúwa rẹ̀."
  25,56,"A kò sì rán ọ níṣẹ́ tayọ kí o jẹ́ oníròó-ìdùnnú àti olùkìlọ̀."
  25,57,"Sọ pé: “Èmi kò bèèrè owó-ọ̀yà kan lọ́wọ́ yín lórí rẹ̀ àfi ẹni tí ó bá fẹ́ mú ọ̀nà (dáadáa) tọ̀ lọ sí ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ̀.”1 {1}",1:[Ìyẹn ni pé, bí ó tilẹ̀ jẹ́ pé kò sí Òjíṣẹ́ tàbí Ànábì kan tí ó ń gba owó-ọ̀yà lọ́wọ́ ìjọ rẹ̀ lórí iṣẹ́ tí Allāhu fi rán an níṣẹ́ sí wọn, iṣẹ́ olóore ni fún ẹnikẹ́ni láti máa fún Òjíṣẹ́ tí Allāhu rán sí wọn lọ́rẹ. Ọrẹ sì yàtọ̀ sí owó-ọ̀yà.]
  26,28,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “(Allāhu ni) Olúwa ibùyọ òòrùn, ibùwọ̀ òòrùn àti ohunkóhun tó ń bẹ láààrin àwọn méjèèjì, tí ẹ bá máa ń ṣe làákàyè.”"
  26,29,"(Fir‘aon) wí pé: “Dájúdájú tí o bá fi lè jọ́sìn fún ọlọ́hun kan yàtọ̀ sí mi, dájúdájú mo máa sọ ọ́ di ara àwọn ẹlẹ́wọ̀n.”"
  26,30,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé mo mú kiní kan tó yanjú wá fún ọ ńkọ́?”"
  27,1,"Tọ̄ sīn. (Allāhu ló mọ ohun tí Ó gbàlérò pẹ̀lú àwọn háràfí náà.)Ìwọ̀nyí ni àwọn āyah al-Ƙur’ān àti (àwọn āyah) Tírà tó ń yanjú ọ̀rọ̀ ẹ̀dá. {1}",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al Baƙọrah; 2:1.]
  27,2,"(Ó jẹ́) ìmọ̀nà àti ìró ìdùnnú fún àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo,"
  27,3,"àwọn tó ń kírun, tí wọ́n ń yọ zakāh. Àwọn sì ni wọ́n ní àmọ̀dájú nípa Ọjọ́ Ìkẹ́yìn."